<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,1732,2010]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,273,1732,1757]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
<collectingRegion box="[282,302,1734,1758]" country="Nigeria" name="Rivers" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">A</collectingRegion>
black species with yellow head and legs, black undusted frontal triangle, black thorax, the greater part of the pleura heavily grey dusted, the wing long and narrow and the arista (Fig. 4) having the sum of the lengths of the first two segments equal to the length of the third.
</paragraph>
